Type: Package
Package: r2slides
Title: Google Slides/Sheets creation from R
Version: 0.0.9025
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Hubbs", , "adam@y2analytics.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create Google Slides from R code. This utilizes the Google
    Slides and Google Sheets API's to create charts and slides from R
    code. It is roughly similar to Officer, but with the Google Suite.
